<#
.SYNOPSIS
    This PowerShell script checks whether the registry key DisableWindowsConsumerFeatures is set to 1 to disable Microsoft consumer experiences on Windows 10, 
    and if not, it creates or updates the key to enforce that setting.

.NOTES
    Author          : Benjamin Lawson
    LinkedIn        : linkedin.com/in/benjamin-lawson06/
    GitHub          : github.com/Benjamin-Lawson23
    Date Created    : 2026-02-17
    Last Modified   : 2026-02-17
    Version         : 1.0
    CVEs            : N/A
    Plugin IDs      : N/A
    STIG-ID         : WN10-AC-000005

.TESTED ON
    Date(s) Tested  : 
    Tested By       : 
